author: Divya Rao
title: Uday Chopra Just Shared The Cutest Photo Of Aditya Chopra
text:
Divya Rao Feb . 23 . 2017 Source: Twitter @Rani_MukerjiFC 
Aditya Chopra , much like his father, Yash Chopra , is known for his amazing work as a director. Whenever you think of an Aditya Chopra film, you think of romance, beautiful women, epic love stories and strong characters… While Chopra’s films are out there for the world to see, he himself is quite the social recluse. Or let’s say ‘media recluse’. Aditya hates being photographed by the media and makes an active effort to stay away from the limelight. 
Uday Chopra just shared this throwback photo of his brother and it’s the cutest! It’s also one of those rare occasions where you’ll find Aditya Chopra’s photo on the Internet! A post shared by Uday Chopra (@udayc) on Feb 21, 2017 at 3:41am PST 
So cute!
